00:22:45,760 --> 00:22:47,120
Is something the matter?

257
00:22:47,120 --> 00:22:49,320
Just talking care of some trouble.

258
00:22:50,780 --> 00:22:52,640
Oh, what?!

259
00:22:52,640 --> 00:22:55,080
I think... there's something there.

260
00:22:55,080 --> 00:22:57,590
Oh, it's fine. I'm just fine.

261
00:22:57,590 --> 00:22:59,950
Is Team Leader Jin going with you, by any chance?

262
00:22:59,950 --> 00:23:02,960
Yes, she's the one who did this, so I need to fix this problem with her.

263
00:23:02,960 --> 00:23:05,170
Please take care of the restaurant.

264
00:23:05,780 --> 00:23:07,670
Welcome.

265
00:23:07,670 --> 00:23:11,020
Oh, Yun Cheol, I'm glad you are here.

266
00:23:11,020 --> 00:23:13,190
Yes, what brings you here?

267
00:23:13,190 --> 00:23:16,620
Oh, we have some urgent off-site business, so please excuse us.

268
00:23:18,520 --> 00:23:21,930
What? What?

269
00:23:21,930 --> 00:23:24,710
What's the matter?

270
00:23:24,710 --> 00:23:26,410
Huh? Oh.

271
00:23:28,140 --> 00:23:31,140
That woman, she's that woman from that time, isn't she?

272
00:23:31,140 --> 00:23:33,490
Honey.

273
00:23:33,490 --> 00:23:36,410
She's not as pretty in real life, compared to the TV.

274
00:23:36,410 --> 00:23:38,900
Honey, let's go.

275
00:23:38,900 --> 00:23:40,520
