 - We estimate Song Yu Min's time of death as 5 am to 7 am yesterday.

290
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:03,870
But right at that time, near the motel,

291
00:25:03,870 --> 00:25:06,620
we found this suspect who was running away.

292
00:25:06,620 --> 00:25:11,330
This person in the video, she's a woman, isn't she?

293
00:25:11,330 --> 00:25:13,460
Based on her clothing, yes.

294
00:25:13,460 --> 00:25:14,990
 It's my wife.

295
00:25:14,990 --> 00:25:20,090
