301
00:25:34,900 --> 00:25:37,940
But you don't have any proof that I wasn't.

302
00:25:37,940 --> 00:25:42,060
Are you sure you were home from 5 am to 7 am yesterday morning?

303
00:25:42,060 --> 00:25:43,760
Do you have a warrant?

304
00:25:43,760 --> 00:25:46,450
Can the police torment someone like this without any evidence at all?

305
00:25:46,450 --> 00:25:48,050
You're not even letting us take care of business off-site.

306
00:25:48,050 --> 00:25:51,090
Why are you investigating us?

307
00:25:51,090 --> 00:25:53,430
Wasn't Song Yu Min's death ruled a suicide?

308
00:25:53,430 --> 00:25:54,690
It's a homicide.

309
00:25:54,690 --> 00:25:57,760
