310
00:25:57,760 --> 00:26:00,840
It seems connected to Sim Jae Gyeong's abduction.

311
00:26:00,840 --> 00:26:05,630
Even after the death of Song Yu Min, the most likely suspect, that case is still under investigation.

312
00:26:05,630 --> 00:26:08,930
Not to mention, Song Yu Min did not work alone.

313
00:26:08,930 --> 00:26:10,640
