322
00:27:04,240 --> 00:27:05,920
Hey.

323
00:27:05,920 --> 00:27:07,630
What?

324
00:27:07,630 --> 00:27:10,250
I understand.

325
00:27:10,250 --> 00:27:12,820
Jae Gyeong.

326
00:27:12,820 --> 00:27:15,970
Omo, you've come?

327
00:27:15,970 --> 00:27:17,660
We came to eat.

328
00:27:17,660 --> 00:27:20,870
Thank you. Enjoy your meal.

329
00:27:20,870 --> 00:27:22,790
Jae Gyeong?

330
00:27:27,130 --> 00:27:30,120
I was so shocked earlier.

331
00:27:30,120 --> 00:27:33,170
