00:30:17,180 --> 00:30:20,350
♫  Love is something I don't have anymore  ♫

376
00:30:20,350 --> 00:30:22,150
What's wrong?

377
00:30:22,850 --> 00:30:25,090
Ah, passport.

378
00:30:26,190 --> 00:30:28,450
You should have told me about this earlier.

379
00:30:28,450 --> 00:30:30,420
Hurry and go.

380
00:31:26,250 --> 00:31:28,150
Chae Rim?

381
00:31:28,150 --> 00:31:30,710
Auntie.

382
00:31:31,570 --> 00:31:35,050
