385
00:31:40,250 --> 00:31:44,920
To thank you for congratulating me when I got out of the hospital.

386
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:46,790
Thank you.

387
00:31:46,790 --> 00:31:48,920
I have one more gift for you.

388
00:31:48,920 --> 00:31:51,050
Another one?

389
00:31:52,550 --> 00:31:54,930
Want to get in the car?

390
00:32:06,330 --> 00:32:10,230
Is this your car, Auntie? Did you get a new one?

391
00:32:10,230 --> 00:32:16,230
No, I borrowed it. To prepare for your other gift.

392
00:32:18,940 --> 00:32:24,210
- Want to eat this? 
 - Thank you for the second gift.

393
00:32:24,210 --> 00:32:29,280
This is just a treat. The real gift is something else.

394
00:32:29,280 --> 00:32:31,360
I'm looking forward to it.

395
