00:33:17,230 --> 00:33:19,950
 Call from: Chae Rim's Mom

400
00:33:23,600 --> 00:33:24,810
What?

401
00:33:24,810 --> 00:33:27,740
I got a text message from Chae Rim.

402
00:33:30,400 --> 00:33:31,470
What?

403
00:33:31,470 --> 00:33:34,200
You're with her right now, aren't you?

404
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:35,860
What did the text message say?

405
00:33:35,860 --> 00:33:40,180
That she met you so she'll spend time with you before she comes home.

406
00:33:40,180 --> 00:33:45,360
