407
00:33:45,360 --> 00:33:48,580
Next time, please contact me beforehand.

408
00:33:48,580 --> 00:33:53,040
Make sure to bring her home by 7 pm, she has school tomorrow.

409
00:33:53,040 --> 00:33:55,620
Okay, I understand. Got it.

410
00:33:55,620 --> 00:33:58,070
I'll bring her home safely, so don't worry.

411
00:33:58,070 --> 00:34:00,330
But what's with you, suddenly?

412
00:34:00,330 --> 00:34:03,220
Why would you just take her at such a random time?

413
00:34:04,950 --> 00:34:08,380
I got it, so I'll hang up now.

