434
00:36:43,320 --> 00:36:46,320
My honey is so smart at times like this.

435
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:48,190
Alright.

436
00:36:58,740 --> 00:37:00,680
I'm done.

437
00:37:10,530 --> 00:37:12,890
Yes, that's the earliest flight.

