00:38:39,160 --> 00:38:40,390
Brother-in-law?

459
00:38:40,390 --> 00:38:42,500
Never mind!

460
00:38:42,500 --> 00:38:48,830
Bring the money right now or I will kill you, too.

461
00:39:17,610 --> 00:39:19,730
You're not really thinking of taking that, are you?

462
00:39:19,730 --> 00:39:23,690
