463
00:39:23,690 --> 00:39:25,470
Sorry. What's wrong is wrong.

464
00:39:25,470 --> 00:39:28,990
If I don't stop my wife now, everyone will be in danger.

465
00:39:36,510 --> 00:39:39,600
No. No!

466
00:39:39,600 --> 00:39:42,020
Don't go.

467
00:39:42,020 --> 00:39:47,400
She's a child. She is not involved in this fight among adults. And she's still alive.

468
00:39:47,400 --> 00:39:49,350
Do I need to explain further?

469
00:39:54,310 --> 00:39:56,400
No!

470
00:40:14,010 --> 00:40:15,880
 Uncle.

471
00:40:20,630 --> 00:40:23,590
 Auntie taught this to me.

472
00:40:25,300 --> 00:40:31,090
 If I'm having unhappy thoughts, hold the candy in my hand.

473
00:40:34,370 --> 00:40:40,530
 If I don't feel better, then unwrap the candy and eat it.

474
00:40:48,700 --> 00:40:52,130
 While eating it, try to let it melt slowly.

475
00:40:58,370 --> 00:41:00,180
 Like this?

476
00:41:04,050 --> 00:41:07,990
 Don't worry, Uncle.

477
00:41:07,990 --> 00:41:10,460
 It will be alright.

478
00:41:16,030 --> 00:41:18,190
