00:44:09,790 --> 00:44:16,190
Is that so? But I want to go further.

501
00:44:16,190 --> 00:44:20,780
Honey, how did you become like this?

502
00:44:21,630 --> 00:44:24,100
When I was young,

503
00:44:24,100 --> 00:44:27,290
I came here often to play.

504
00:44:27,290 --> 00:44:31,360
They raised a goldfish in the office.

505
00:44:32,460 --> 00:44:34,090
Oh, what was its name?

506
00:44:34,090 --> 00:44:36,370
