615
00:54:24,590 --> 00:54:27,030
Appease her gently.

616
00:54:27,030 --> 00:54:30,080
I'll investigate on my own, too.

617
00:54:30,080 --> 00:54:32,790
So what should I do now?

618
00:54:32,800 --> 00:54:35,480
