00:54:35,480 --> 00:54:37,000
And there is only one thing that is important.

620
00:54:37,040 --> 00:54:40,720
No matter what the circumstances are, in the end,

621
00:54:40,720 --> 00:54:43,950
the spouses need to decide for themselves.

622
00:54:45,950 --> 00:54:49,390
But there is one piece of advice I really want to give you.

623
00:54:50,350 --> 00:54:52,240
What is it?

624
00:54:55,290 --> 00:54:58,250
Be careful and don't die.

625
00:54:58,250 --> 00:55:03,020
Because a ferocious dog will bite its owner when it is desperate.

626
00:55:18,540 --> 00:55:20,680
Welcome.

