629
00:55:44,390 --> 00:55:46,090
Have a seat.

630
00:56:05,860 --> 00:56:08,850
- Lieutenant Seo.
 - Ah, yes.

631
00:56:08,850 --> 00:56:12,200
You're still at it? I told you, wrap this case up already.

632
00:56:12,200 --> 00:56:13,610
This isn't a simple suicide.

633
00:56:13,610 --> 00:56:17,690
Won't you go home? Don't get kicked out of your family while taking care of someone else's.

634
00:56:17,690 --> 00:56:21,230
Haven't you heard the saying, "When one's home is happy, all goes well." Don't become like me.

635
00:56:21,230 --> 00:56:24,010
- Take care of your household. 
 - Yes.

636
00:56:24,010 --> 00:56:26,850
- So go home. 
