646
00:56:54,820 --> 00:56:57,180
I think our play area has become even smaller.

647
00:56:57,180 --> 00:56:58,500
Look, look.

648
00:56:58,500 --> 00:57:00,580
Like this. Clean.

649
00:57:00,580 --> 00:57:04,420
If you clean up, ta-da. More space to play.

650
00:57:04,420 --> 00:57:08,610
If you buy less stuff, won't you have less to put away?

651
00:57:15,920 --> 00:57:21,070
Adults don't ever make sense. Do they, Hyeong?

652
00:57:21,070 --> 00:57:23,080
Let's play.

653
00:57:23,080 --> 00:57:24,940
Catch me!

654
00:57:24,940 --> 00:57:27,680
Please don't run.

655
00:57:41,090 --> 00:57:44,230
 Catch me if you can!

656
00:57:54,980 --> 00:57:58,230
Are you trying to hit me?

